node.title: This week’s news quiz theme is 'Who am I?' Reckon you know?
node.alt: A woman in a face mask looks out the window of a red double decker bus at Christmas lights
node.description: Every week, we ask you if you’ve been paying attention to the news. We bet you thought we meant the words, right? Well, here’s a test — this week, did you take note of who was saying what?
node.content: ["CHECKED FOR FRIDAY News Quiz November 19Can you put some names to faces and come away with news quiz glory?", "Time to test your knowledge."]
